description: This file defines an enumeration for consultation statuses, a data model class 'Consultation' with fields for consultation details, including methods for JSON serialization and deserialization, and a utility function for converting string to enum.

classes.name: Consultation
classes.description: A data model representing a medical consultation, including identifiers, scheduled time, symptoms, notes, and status.

methods.name: statusFromString
methods.description: Converts a string to the corresponding 'ConsultationStatus' enum value.

methods.name: Consultation.fromJson
methods.description: Factory constructor that creates a 'Consultation' instance from a JSON map.
